{"tid":1164193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有線新聞刺針］依家有未成年青年食大麻，透過ig買貨","createTime":"2019-05-21T01:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T05:41:17.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"15dfc9f08d997f3237b0a7445f933ef2543d3310","tid":1164193,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:53:38.000Z","msg":"值得一睇<br />\n有線記者試埋約人出嚟交收<br />\n<br />\n【青少年買大麻有多容易？】<br />\n根據禁毒處調查，2017/18年度，在報稱曾經吸毒的中學生當中，有近八成人表示大麻是最常吸食的毒品，數字比四年前同一調查多出兩成，吸食大麻的青少年多了，而大麻在一些青少年圈子亦流傳得很容易。「新聞刺針」接觸了一些未成年個案，還有大麻賣家，看看他們怎樣供貨予青少年。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1215581751948197&amp;id=153300521509664&amp;__tn__=%2As%2As-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1215581751948197%26id%3D153300521509664%26__tn__%3D%252As%252As-R&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=0205e598\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1215581751948197&amp;id=153300521509664&amp;__tn__=%2As%2As-R</a>"},{"pid":"3da963054a23dbc9da2725c45cc4746b5b7bc8bb","tid":1164193,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:59:39.000Z","msg":"巧超🚬😎"},{"pid":"5c22e1d06e72195c6e9d929fea1f33b54d73fe12","tid":1164193,"uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ox6hWUC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOx6hWUC.png&h=0ae5e8b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7abb7a98f756adaa2cde4ccba58eacc7df13a5d0","tid":1164193,"uid":249885,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:36:27.000Z","msg":"啲撚樣係要食呢啲野搞到自己周身病痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6150b20ba5e43ed044dfca4afda614dbe33633a","tid":1164193,"uid":2